# Frontend env (see backend in ../web technolagy/)
#
# Local: VITE_USE_API=true in .env.development. Add VITE_API_BASE_URL if you need the browser to call the API directly.
# Production build: set VITE_USE_API=true and VITE_API_BASE_URL to your deployed API URL (no trailing slash).
# Backend CLIENT_ORIGIN should list your site origin(s); optional CORS_ALLOW_LOCALHOST for dev against prod API.
